data.text:
Wilhelmina is sold as a set.

This luxurious ensemble marries contemporary design with timeless elegance, offering a sophisticated look that enhances your silhouette and exudes refined style. The off-the-shoulder crop top features delicate pleating, creating a flattering neckline that highlights your shoulders and collarbone. Complemented by the high-waist pleated pants, this set provides a tailored fit that accentuates your figure while ensuring ultimate comfort and sophistication.

Get ready to jet set to exotic destinations with this resort pleated coordinating set. From palm leaves to exotic fruits, these pieces will make you feel like you're on a permanent vacation.
